| # | Severity | File | Description | Confidence |
|---|----------|------|-------------|------------|
| 1 | Critical | `interactService.js` L276-288 | Chain resolution silently falls back to wrong user on error/deleted original | 95 |
| 2 | Critical | `interactService.js` L276-288 | Resolved original post privacy is never re-validated | 92 |
| 3 | Important | `PostCards.jsx` L711 | Repost-of-repost opens modal with reposter's data instead of original author | 88 |
| 4 | Important | `PostCards.jsx` L723-725 | Missing optional chaining on `.count` crashes render for zero-count repost cards | 90 |
| 5 | Important | `ContentView.jsx` L528-539 | Repost success notification shares state/timer with bookmark toast, can be clobbered | 82 |
| 6 | Important | `RepostModal.jsx` L45,57,100 | `onClose` receives `SyntheticEvent` on dismiss instead of nothing/undefined | 85 |

